{{Infobox journal | title = Zeitschrift für die Neutestamentliche Wissenschaft | cover = ZNW-cover.gif | editor = Michael Wolter | discipline = [[New Testament]] | language = English, French, German | abbreviation = Z. Neutest. Wiss. | publisher = [[Walter de Gruyter]] | country = | frequency = Biannually | history = 1900-present | openaccess = | impact = | impact-year = | website = http://www.degruyter.de/journals/znw/detail.cfm | link1 = http://www.reference-global.com/toc/zntw/current | link1-name = Online access | link2 = http://www.reference-global.com/loi/zntw | link2-name = Online archive | JSTOR = | OCLC = 1773087 | LCCN = a20000462 | CODEN = | ISSN = 0044-2615 | eISSN = 1613-009X }} The '''''Zeitschrift für die Neutestamentliche Wissenschaft und die Kunde der älteren Kirche''''' (English: ''Journal for New Testament Studies and the Ancient Church'') is a biannual [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] that was established in 1900. It is published by [[Walter de Gruyter]]. The focus of the journal is the historical investigation of early [[Christianity]], especially on the [[New Testament]] and nascent Christianity through to the [[Patristic]] period. The current [[editor-in-chief]] is Michael Wolter. Articles are in German, English, or French.
A related journal from the same publisher is the ''[[Zeitschrift für die Alttestamentliche Wissenschaft]]''.
